  <brief_title>High-intensity Exercise Training or Multidisciplinary Treatment in Extremely Obese Adolescents</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reducing Cardiovascular Risk Factors In Overweight Adolescents: Multidisciplinary Treatment and Intensity Controlled Interval Training</official_title>
  <sponsors>
